@page "/design"
@layout PgmStudio.Client.Layout.EditorLayout
@using PgmStudio.Client.Pages.EditorActivities
@inject IJSRuntime JS

@* Living UI reference — verbatim port of studio/templates/design.html (the design system
   showcase). Uses tokens/components/editor/design CSS. *@

<div class="editor-page">

<div id="topbar" class="topbar">
  <a href="/" class="topbar-breadcrumb-home" title="Back to dashboard">
    <i data-lucide="house"></i>
    <span>Studio</span>
  </a>
  <span class="topbar-sep">›</span>
  <span class="topbar-crumb">UI Reference</span>
  <div class="topbar-right">
    <span class="ds-file-list">tokens.css · components.css · editor.css</span>
    <ThemeToggle />
  </div>
</div>

<div id="ds-layout">
  <nav id="ds-nav" aria-label="UI reference sections">
    <div class="ds-nav-group">Reference</div>
    <a href="#foundations">Foundations</a>
    <a href="#panels">Panel anatomy</a>
    <a href="#content">Panel content</a>
    <a href="#workspaces">Workspaces</a>
    <a href="#canvas">Canvas</a>
    <a href="#states">States</a>
    <a href="#suggestion">Smart suggestion</a>
    <a href="#rules">Usage rules</a>
  </nav>

  <main id="ds-main">
    <header class="ds-intro">
      <p class="ds-kicker">Production-backed examples</p>
      <h1>Studio UI Reference</h1>
      <p>
        These examples use the same classes and nesting as Dashboard, Editor, and
        Sketch. Copy the structure, keep IDs as JavaScript handles, and add new
        component CSS only when no reference here fits.
      </p>
    </header>

    <section class="ds-section" id="foundations">
      <div class="ds-section-heading">
        <div>
          <p class="ds-kicker">01</p>
          <h2>Foundations</h2>
        </div>
        <p>Use tokens for every repeated color, spacing, radius, shadow, and transition.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="ds-subsection">
        <h3>Surfaces and text</h3>
        <div class="ds-swatches">
          <div class="ds-swatch"><span class="ds-swatch-chip ds-bg-base"></span><code>--bg-base</code><small>Page background</small></div>
          <div class="ds-swatch"><span class="ds-swatch-chip ds-bg-panel"></span><code>--bg-panel</code><small>Shell and panels</small></div>
          <div class="ds-swatch"><span class="ds-swatch-chip ds-bg-deep"></span><code>--bg-deep</code><small>Recessed surface</small></div>
          <div class="ds-swatch"><span class="ds-swatch-chip ds-bg-canvas"></span><code>--bg-canvas</code><small>Map viewport</small></div>
          <div class="ds-swatch"><span class="ds-swatch-chip ds-bg-selected"></span><code>--bg-selected</code><small>Selection</small></div>
          <div class="ds-swatch"><span class="ds-swatch-chip ds-text-muted"></span><code>--text-muted</code><small>Quietest text</small></div>
          <div class="ds-swatch"><span class="ds-swatch-chip ds-text-primary"></span><code>--text-primary</code><small>Body text</small></div>
          <div class="ds-swatch"><span class="ds-swatch-chip ds-text-strong"></span><code>--text-strong</code><small>Headings / active</small></div>
          <div class="ds-swatch"><span class="ds-swatch-chip ds-accent"></span><code>--accent</code><small>Focus and primary</small></div>
          <div class="ds-swatch"><span class="ds-swatch-chip ds-error"></span><code>--color-error</code><small>Destructive/error</small></div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="ds-subsection">
        <h3>Theming</h3>
        <p class="ds-theming-note">
          Two themes share one token set. Dark is the default; <code>&lt;html data-theme="light"&gt;</code>
          — toggled by the sun / moon button in the top bar — overrides only the <em>colour</em> tokens,
          while spacing, radii, type, and motion are shared. Toggle the theme to preview the swatches above
          live. The fixed game palettes (chat, dye, team, wool, and block-overlay colours) live outside CSS,
          so they stay the same in both themes.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="ds-subsection">
        <h3>Spacing rhythm</h3>
        <div class="ds-spacing">
          <div><span class="ds-space ds-space-1"></span><code>--space-1</code><small>4px</small></div>
          <div><span class="ds-space ds-space-2"></span><code>--space-2</code><small>8px</small></div>
          <div><span class="ds-space ds-space-3"></span><code>--space-3</code><small>12px</small></div>
          <div><span class="ds-space ds-space-4"></span><code>--space-4</code><small>16px</small></div>
          <div><span class="ds-space ds-space-5"></span><code>--space-5</code><small>20px</small></div>
          <div><span class="ds-space ds-space-6"></span><code>--space-6</code><small>24px</small></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="ds-section" id="panels">
      <div class="ds-section-heading">
        <div>
          <p class="ds-kicker">02</p>
          <h2>Panel anatomy</h2>
        </div>
        <p>A panel is a stack of sections. Each section has a header, body, and optional footer.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="ds-example-grid">
        <article class="ds-example">
          <div class="ds-example-label">Left sidebar form</div>
          <div class="ds-panel-frame">
            <div class="workspace-scroll">
              <section class="panel-section">
                <div class="section-header section-header--ruled">
                  <h2 class="section-title">Map Identity</h2>
                </div>
                <div class="section-body">
                  <div class="field">
                    <label class="field-label" for="ds-map-name">Map Name <span class="field-required">*</span></label>
                    <input id="ds-map-name" class="field-input" value="Annealing V"/>
                  </div>
                  <div class="field-row">
                    <div class="field">
                      <label class="field-label" for="ds-version">Version</label>
                      <input id="ds-version" class="field-input" value="1.0.0"/>
                    </div>
                    <div class="field field--compact">
                      <label class="field-label" for="ds-mode">Mode</label>
                      <input id="ds-mode" class="field-input" value="ctw" disabled/>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="section-footer">
                  <button class="action-btn action-btn--primary">Save changes</button>
                  <span class="panel-save-status">Saved</span>
                </div>
              </section>
            </div>
          </div>
        </article>

        <article class="ds-example">
          <div class="ds-example-label">Right inspector</div>
          <div class="ds-panel-frame">
            <div class="workspace-scroll">
              <div class="panel-stack">
                <section class="panel-section">
                  <div class="detail-header">
                    <span class="geo-type-icon detail-icon--muted"><i data-lucide="cylinder"></i></span>
                    <span class="detail-label detail-label--mono">red-spawn</span>
                    <span class="badge badge--neutral">Cylinder</span>
                  </div>
                  <div class="section-body">
                    <div class="field">
                      <label class="field-label">Base</label>
                      <div class="ctrl-row">
                        <div class="coord-field"><span class="coord-prefix">X</span><input class="coord-input" value="48.5"/></div>
                        <div class="coord-field"><span class="coord-prefix">Y</span><input class="coord-input" value="9"/></div>
                        <div class="coord-field"><span class="coord-prefix">Z</span><input class="coord-input" value="-187"/></div>
                      </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="field">
                      <label class="field-label">Dimensions</label>
                      <div class="ctrl-row">
                        <div class="coord-field"><span class="coord-prefix">R</span><input class="coord-input" value="0.5"/></div>
                        <div class="coord-field"><span class="coord-prefix">H</span><input class="coord-input" value="2"/></div>
                      </div>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                  <div class="section-footer section-footer--separated">
                    <button class="action-btn action-btn--danger action-btn--fill">Delete region</button>
                  </div>
                </section>
                <section class="panel-section">
                  <div class="section-header section-header--ruled">
                    <h2 class="section-title">Spawn Assignment</h2>
                  </div>
                  <div class="field">
                    <label class="field-label">Team</label>
                    <select class="field-input"><option>Red</option></select>
                  </div>
                </section>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </article>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="ds-section" id="content">
      <div class="ds-section-heading">
        <div>
          <p class="ds-kicker">03</p>
          <h2>Panel content</h2>
        </div>
        <p>Use explicit wrappers for repeated content so spacing belongs to the collection.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="ds-example-grid">
        <article class="ds-example">
          <div class="ds-example-label">Field row</div>
          <div class="ds-panel-frame">
            <div class="workspace-scroll">
              <section class="panel-section">
                <div class="section-header section-header--ruled">
                  <h2 class="section-title">Map Version</h2>
                </div>
                <div class="field-row">
                  <div class="field">
                    <label class="field-label" for="ds-version-major">Version</label>
                    <input id="ds-version-major" class="field-input" value="1.0.0"/>
                  </div>
                  <div class="field field--compact">
                    <label class="field-label" for="ds-version-mode">Mode</label>
                    <input id="ds-version-mode" class="field-input" value="ctw" disabled/>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </section>
            </div>
          </div>
        </article>

        <article class="ds-example">
          <div class="ds-example-label">Panel list</div>
          <div class="ds-panel-frame">
            <div class="workspace-scroll">
              <section class="panel-section">
                <div class="section-header section-header--ruled">
                  <h2 class="section-title">Teams</h2>
                  <button class="action-btn">+ Add Team</button>
                </div>
                <div class="panel-list">
                  <div class="list-row list-row--selected"><span class="list-swatch ds-team-red"></span><span class="list-label">Red</span><span class="badge badge--success">Ready</span></div>
                  <div class="list-row"><span class="list-swatch ds-team-blue"></span><span class="list-label">Blue</span><span class="list-tag">20 players</span></div>
                  <div class="list-row list-row--compact"><span class="geo-type-icon"><i data-lucide="cylinder"></i></span><span class="list-label list-label--mono">red-spawn</span><span class="list-tag">Red</span></div>
                </div>
              </section>
            </div>
          </div>
        </article>

        <article class="ds-example">
          <div class="ds-example-label">Author list</div>
          <div class="ds-panel-frame">
            <div class="workspace-scroll">
              <section class="panel-section">
                <div class="section-header section-header--ruled">
                  <h2 class="section-title">Authors <span class="field-required">*</span></h2>
                  <button class="action-btn">+ Add</button>
                </div>
                <div class="author-list">
                  <div class="author-row">
                    <span class="author-avatar"></span>
                    <input class="field-input author-name" value="fakejustcupcakes"/>
                    <input class="field-input author-contribution" placeholder="Contribution (optional)"/>
                    <button class="btn-remove" title="Remove"><i data-lucide="x"></i></button>
                  </div>
                  <div class="author-row">
                    <span class="author-avatar"></span>
                    <input class="field-input author-name" value="killAce"/>
                    <input class="field-input author-contribution" value="Terrain"/>
                    <button class="btn-remove" title="Remove"><i data-lucide="x"></i></button>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </section>
            </div>
          </div>
        </article>

        <article class="ds-example">
          <div class="ds-example-label">Control list</div>
          <div class="ds-panel-frame">
            <div class="workspace-scroll">
              <section class="panel-section">
                <div class="section-header section-header--ruled">
                  <h2 class="section-title">Overlays</h2>
                </div>
                <div class="control-list">
                  <label class="check-row"><input type="checkbox" checked/>Mirror preview</label>
                  <label class="check-row"><input type="checkbox"/>Shapes overlay</label>
                  <label class="check-row"><input type="checkbox" checked/>Chunk grid</label>
                </div>
              </section>
            </div>
          </div>
        </article>

        <article class="ds-example">
          <div class="ds-example-label">Region tree</div>
          <div class="ds-panel-frame">
            <div class="workspace-scroll">
              <section class="panel-section">
                <div class="section-header section-header--ruled">
                  <h2 class="section-title">Wool Regions</h2>
                </div>
                <div class="region-tree">
                  <div class="geo-row geo-row--selected">
                    <span class="geo-indent">
                      <button class="collapse-btn" title="Collapse"><i data-lucide="chevron-down"></i></button>
                    </span>
                    <span class="geo-type-icon"><i data-lucide="combine"></i></span>
                    <span class="geo-label">purple-wool-room</span>
                  </div>
                  <div class="geo-row geo-row--selected-child">
                    <span class="geo-indent"><span class="indent-pipe"></span></span>
                    <span class="geo-type-icon"><i data-lucide="box"></i></span>
                    <span class="geo-label">purple-wool-bounds</span>
                  </div>
                  <div class="geo-row">
                    <span class="geo-indent"></span>
                    <span class="geo-type-icon"><i data-lucide="cylinder"></i></span>
                    <span class="geo-label">orange-wool-room</span>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </section>
            </div>
          </div>
        </article>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="ds-section" id="workspaces">
      <div class="ds-section-heading">
        <div>
          <p class="ds-kicker">04</p>
          <h2>Workspaces</h2>
        </div>
        <p>The sidebar and inspector share the same panel construction. Handles sit directly beside resizable panels.</p>
      </div>

      <article class="ds-example">
        <div class="ds-example-label">Three-column activity workspace</div>
        <div class="ds-workspace-frame">
          <div class="workspace">
            <div class="workspace-sidebar">
              <div class="workspace-scroll">
                <section class="panel-section">
                  <div class="section-header section-header--ruled"><h2 class="section-title">Islands</h2></div>
                  <div class="panel-list">
                    <div class="list-row list-row--selected"><span class="geo-type-icon"><i data-lucide="layers"></i></span><span class="list-label">Center</span></div>
                    <div class="list-row"><span class="geo-type-icon"><i data-lucide="layers"></i></span><span class="list-label">Team island</span></div>
                  </div>
                </section>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="sidebar-handle"></div>
            <div class="workspace-canvas">
              <div class="canvas-subbar">
                <div class="canvas-toolbar">
                  <button class="draw-tool-btn draw-tool-btn--active"><i data-lucide="hand"></i></button>
                  <button class="draw-tool-btn"><i data-lucide="mouse-pointer-2"></i></button>
                  <button class="draw-tool-btn"><i data-lucide="rectangle-horizontal"></i></button>
                </div>
                <span class="canvas-cursor">X 128 · Z -64</span>
                <div class="canvas-subbar-right"><span class="canvas-zoom">100%</span></div>
              </div>
              <div class="canvas-surface ds-canvas-sample">
                <span class="ds-axis ds-axis-x"></span>
                <span class="ds-axis ds-axis-z"></span>
                <span class="ds-region-sample"></span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="sidebar-handle"></div>
            <div class="workspace-inspector">
              <div class="workspace-scroll">
                <section class="panel-section">
                  <div class="detail-header">
                    <span class="geo-type-icon detail-icon--muted"><i data-lucide="rectangle-horizontal"></i></span>
                    <span class="detail-label">Team island</span>
                    <span class="badge badge--neutral">Rectangle</span>
                  </div>
                  <div class="field"><label class="field-label">Operation</label><span class="badge badge--success">Add</span></div>
                </section>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </article>
    </section>

    <section class="ds-section" id="canvas">
      <div class="ds-section-heading">
        <div>
          <p class="ds-kicker">05</p>
          <h2>Canvas subbar</h2>
        </div>
        <p>Keep tools left, transient coordinates centered, and persistent status right.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="ds-canvas-bar-example canvas-subbar">
        <div class="canvas-toolbar">
          <button class="draw-tool-btn draw-tool-btn--active" title="Pan"><i data-lucide="hand"></i></button>
          <button class="draw-tool-btn" title="Select"><i data-lucide="mouse-pointer-2"></i></button>
          <button class="draw-tool-btn" title="Rectangle"><i data-lucide="rectangle-horizontal"></i></button>
          <button class="draw-tool-btn" title="Circle"><i data-lucide="circle"></i></button>
        </div>
        <div class="subbar-sep"></div>
        <div class="canvas-toolbar">
          <button class="draw-tool-btn draw-tool-btn--op-add"><i data-lucide="plus-square"></i><span class="draw-tool-label">Add</span></button>
          <button class="draw-tool-btn"><i data-lucide="minus-square"></i><span class="draw-tool-label">Sub</span></button>
        </div>
        <span class="canvas-cursor">X 128 · Z -64</span>
        <div class="canvas-subbar-right"><span class="canvas-zoom">100%</span></div>
      </div>

      <div class="ds-subsection" style="margin-top:var(--space-5)">
        <h3>Flow bar (wizard sub-steps)</h3>
        <p class="ds-theming-note">A clean wizard sub-step strip for guided multi-step activities — a
           left-aligned <strong>phase-identity cluster</strong> (<code>flow-bar-phase</code>: the current
           phase's icon + name), then flat-text sub-step labels with an accent underline on the active one
           and a check on completed ones, then Back/Next on the right (Back disabled at the first step).
           It is its <strong>own strip</strong> (<code>flow-bar</code>) above the workspace — never inside the
           <code>canvas-subbar</code>, which keeps its draw toolbar. Use it instead of numbered-circle step bars.</p>
        <div class="flow-bar">
          <div class="flow-bar-phase"><i data-lucide="goal"></i><span>Wools</span></div>
          <div class="flow-steps">
            <button class="flow-step flow-step--done"><i data-lucide="check"></i>Colours</button>
            <button class="flow-step flow-step--active">Spawn &amp; room</button>
            <button class="flow-step">Monuments</button>
          </div>
          <div class="flow-bar-actions">
            <button class="action-btn">Back</button>
            <button class="action-btn action-btn--primary">Next</button>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="ds-section" id="states">
      <div class="ds-section-heading">
        <div>
          <p class="ds-kicker">06</p>
          <h2>Actions and states</h2>
        </div>
        <p>Use one vocabulary for actions, status, empty content, validation, and confidence meters.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="ds-state-row">
        <button class="action-btn">Secondary</button>
        <button class="action-btn action-btn--primary">Primary</button>
        <button class="action-btn action-btn--warn">Pending</button>
        <button class="action-btn action-btn--danger">Delete</button>
        <span class="badge badge--success">Ready</span>
        <span class="badge badge--warning">Review</span>
        <span class="badge badge--error">Invalid</span>
        <span class="badge badge--neutral">Cylinder</span>
        <span class="badge badge--dim">Optional</span>
      </div>
      <div class="ds-state-grid">
        <div class="panel-warning">The selected region overlaps the map boundary.</div>
        <div class="ds-empty-sample"><p class="panel-empty-msg">Select a team or region to inspect.</p></div>
        <div class="field">
          <label class="field-label">ID</label>
          <input class="field-input field-input--error" value="spawn-red"/>
          <div class="field-error">Region ID "spawn-red" is already in use.</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      @* Meter — thin confidence/score bar (track + .meter-fill; width inline, colour band by modifier).
         Used for ranked monument suggestions. *@
      <div class="ds-state-grid" style="margin-top:var(--space-4)">
        <div class="field"><label class="field-label">Confidence · high <span class="text-muted text-sm">0.90</span></label><div class="meter"><div class="meter-fill" style="width:90%"></div></div></div>
        <div class="field"><label class="field-label">Confidence · mid <span class="text-muted text-sm">0.55</span></label><div class="meter"><div class="meter-fill meter-fill--mid" style="width:55%"></div></div></div>
        <div class="field"><label class="field-label">Confidence · low <span class="text-muted text-sm">0.25</span></label><div class="meter"><div class="meter-fill meter-fill--low" style="width:25%"></div></div></div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="ds-section" id="suggestion">
      <div class="ds-section-heading">
        <div>
          <p class="ds-kicker">07</p>
          <h2>Smart suggestion</h2>
        </div>
        <p>Sparkle-headed callout for studio-inferred actions (symmetry → teams, wiring, wools).
           Reusable <code>&lt;SmartSuggestion&gt;</code> — header (icon + title + badge), body, accept/dismiss.
           The suggested-team preview is always a 2-column grid (2 teams → one row, 4 → two).</p>
      </div>
      <div class="ds-sug-sample">
        <SmartSuggestion Header="Smart Suggestion" Badge="rot 90" AcceptLabel="Create 4 teams" RejectLabel="Dismiss">
          <p class="smart-suggestion__text">90° rotational symmetry suggests four teams.</p>
          <div class="smart-suggestion-teams">
            <div class="smart-suggestion-team"><span class="list-swatch list-swatch--sm" style="background:#FF5555"></span>Red Team</div>
            <div class="smart-suggestion-team"><span class="list-swatch list-swatch--sm" style="background:#5555FF"></span>Blue Team</div>
            <div class="smart-suggestion-team"><span class="list-swatch list-swatch--sm" style="background:#55FF55"></span>Green Team</div>
            <div class="smart-suggestion-team"><span class="list-swatch list-swatch--sm" style="background:#FFFF55"></span>Yellow Team</div>
          </div>
        </SmartSuggestion>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="ds-section" id="rules">
      <div class="ds-section-heading">
        <div>
          <p class="ds-kicker">08</p>
          <h2>Usage rules</h2>
        </div>
        <p>The short version. Full contract lives in <code>docs/contracts/ui-conventions.md</code>.</p>
      </div>
      <table class="ds-rules-table">
        <thead><tr><th>Do</th><th>Don't</th></tr></thead>
        <tbody>
          <tr><td>Copy a rendered reference structure.</td><td>Create activity-specific panel spacing.</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Use classes for layout and IDs for JavaScript.</td><td>Patch shared layout with ID selectors.</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Wrap repeated rows in the matching list class.</td><td>Put margins on each repeated child.</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Use `.section-footer` for panel actions.</td><td>Inject widths and margins from JavaScript.</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Add a production example here with a new component.</td><td>Build a separate visual mock of the component.</td></tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>
    </section>
  </main>
</div>

</div>
